    <is_fda_regulated_device>No</is_fda_regulated_device>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a Phase 3, international, multicenter, open-label, long-term extension study. The&#xD;
      primary objective of this study is to evaluate the long-term safety and tolerability of oral&#xD;
      edaravone in subjects with Amyotrophic Lateral Sclerosis (ALS) for up to 96 weeks.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
